# Timer
1.Description of all files in this directory

a. driver.c - This file makes a tcp connection to timer.c and gives instruction to timer.c.
Instructions are of the format : 
startTimer(timevalue,#sequencenumber)
b. timer.c - This file maintains a list of time nodes which represents the time value for each sequence number.

2. Compilation: Go to timer directory within the project home directory.Use below script,
make

3. Running : Open two terminals, one for driver and the other for timer.
--> timer terminal:
./timer <port-number>

--> driver terminal:
./driver <ip-number-of-timer> <timer-process-port-number>
